  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK985">
<l>āṟṟuvā rāṟṟal paṇita latucāṉṟōr</l>
<l>māṟṟārai māṟṟum paṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Stooping (to inferiors) is the strength of those who can accomplish (an undertaking) and that is the weapon with which the great avert their foes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
